X:1
T:Range Walk — Great Highland Pipe (chanter)
C:Tony Koop / sheet-music skill (warmup)
M:4/4
L:1/4
Q:1/4=70
K:Amix
H:All 9 chanter notes, ascending then descending. Slow and even —
H:tone first, then speed. NO RESTS. Hold the final low A as long as
H:the bag will allow.
% Ascending — low G to high A
G A B c | d e f g | a4 |
% Descending — high A to low G
a g f e | d c B A | G4 |
